sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor       User as User
    participant FE    as Frontend<br/>(Next.js)
    participant BE    as Backend<br/>(NestJS)
    participant DB    as Database

    %% ── Phase 1: Update Profile Details & Avatar/Cover ─────────────
    rect rgb(224, 242, 254)
        Note over User,DB: Phase 1 — Update Profile Details & Avatar/Cover

        User ->>+ FE : Select avatar/cover files, enter details, click "Save"
        FE ->> FE : Validate sizes and preview updates locally
        
        opt Avatar attached
            FE ->>+ BE : POST /api/uploads (multipart/form-data) — imgType: square
            BE ->> BE : Save avatar to Cloudinary & generate secure URL
            BE -->>- FE : 201 Created — { filename: avatarPath }
        end

        opt Cover attached
            FE ->>+ BE : POST /api/uploads (multipart/form-data) — imgType: wide
            BE ->> BE : Save cover to Cloudinary & generate secure URL
            BE -->>- FE : 201 Created — { filename: coverPath }
        end

        FE ->>+ BE : PATCH /api/users/me { displayName, bio, img?, cover?, ... }
        Note over BE : JwtAuthGuard + BannedUserGuard
        
        BE ->>+ DB : Update User record (prisma.user.update)
        DB -->>- BE : Updated User record
        BE -->>- FE : 200 OK — Updated user details JSON

        FE ->> FE : Redirect to user's profile (window.location.href)
        FE -->>- User : Display profile page with updated public info
    end

    %% ── Phase 2: View Profile Activity History ──────────────────────
    rect rgb(236, 253, 245)
        Note over User,DB: Phase 2 — View Profile Activity History

        User ->>+ FE : Click on profile page / Switch activity feed tab (Posts/Replies/Media/Likes)
        
        FE ->>+ BE : GET /api/users/:username (Fetch target profile info)
        BE ->>+ DB : Query user & block status (assertNotBlockedPair)
        DB -->>- BE : Target user profile record
        BE -->>- FE : 200 OK — Profile metadata

        FE ->>+ BE : GET /api/users/:username/posts?tab=tabName&cursor=1
        BE ->>+ DB : Query posts / comments by filter tab (posts, replies, etc.)
        DB -->>- BE : List of items (e.g. posts, comment replies) & total count
        BE -->>- FE : 200 OK — { posts[], hasMore, nextCursor }
        FE -->> User : Render initial activity list in InfiniteScroll list

        User ->> FE : Scroll down activity list to load more history
        FE ->>+ BE : GET /api/users/:username/posts?tab=tabName&cursor=2
        BE ->>+ DB : Query next page of profile activities
        DB -->>- BE : Next page items list
        BE -->>- FE : 200 OK — { posts[], hasMore }
        FE -->>- User : Append new activity items to history feed
    end
